#. </p><h5></h5><p><a class="sc" id="58"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.65"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:75.1"
msgid "Yathā vā paneke bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā saddhādeyyāni bhojanāni bhuñjitvā te evarūpaṃ bījagāmabhūtagāmasamārambhaṃ anuyuttā viharanti."
